 the apparent discrepancy between\nour result and those reported in previous studies depends on the method used to\navoid the convective runaways (the so called breathing pulses), which are\nusually encountered in modeling late stage of core He-burning phase.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Oct 2002 17:18:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
